30 class CachedResourceClient {

33         BaseResourceType,
34         ImageType,
35         FontType,
36         StyleSheetType,
37         SVGDocumentType,
38         RawResourceType
39     };
40 
41     virtual ~CachedResourceClient() = default;
42     virtual void notifyFinished(CachedResource&) { }
43     virtual void deprecatedDidReceiveCachedResource(CachedResource&) { }
44     virtual bool isXMLHttpRequest() const { return false; }
45 
46     static CachedResourceClientType expectedType() { return BaseResourceType; }
47     virtual CachedResourceClientType resourceClientType() const { return expectedType(); }
48     virtual bool shouldMarkAsReferenced() const { return true; }
49 
50 protected:
51     CachedResourceClient() = default;
52 };
